{"tid":2094704,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"林鄭月娥：有指港區國安法要經立法會程序是痴人說夢話","createTime":"2020-07-05T01:01:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-05T05:56:15.000Z","uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"184c9dc51a7820be1aa5c9051a4620361db83d4f","tid":2094704,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T01:01:08.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥在社交專頁表示，立法會理性討論施政的空間已愈來愈少，外國官員和議員批評《港區國安法》，認為立法要經過香港立法會的程序，是「痴人說夢話」。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥又說，這些外國官員和議員的本國，無論是單一制或聯邦制，都是由中央或聯邦政府直接負責分裂國家或顛覆國家政權等國家安全罪行的立法，不會假手於地方政府，而這次中央把維護國家安全的主要責任交給特區，是對「一國兩制」的堅持和對特區的高度信任。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1535826-20200704.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1535826-20200704.htm&d=IQhlkTl0XfvqnQYO1cGwmjIStCm0mHK7%2Bbmf%2BnNiY0c%3D&h=86ee37b1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1535826-20200704.htm&h=818e20c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1535826-20200704.htm</a>"},{"pid":"f9fe7fd19ac26037bc35d0daa20c90b5a1836f45","tid":2094704,"uid":153722,"like":0,"dislike":27,"score":-27,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T01:16:24.000Z","msg":"都是由中央或聯邦政府直接負責分裂國家或顛覆國家政權等國家安全罪行的立法，不會假手於地方政府<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n依句我又認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係法律條文離譜含糊兼廣泛，<br />\n加上執行者嘅問題<br />\n加上政府呢一年既處事方式<br />\n<br />\n先令到個國安法咁大鑊姐"},{"pid":"b0f854ea7e0f18a0b450d788a5646292995c5068","tid":2094704,"uid":69872,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T01:16:47.000Z","msg":"人地有民主 我地有冇民主？"},{"pid":"c26898e4cd9b29771f54cde7b3d2e7d76647d56b","tid":2094704,"uid":224533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T01:28:04.000Z","msg":"林奠幾時出石頭？"},{"pid":"c1cbdffc06edfd5208b018b0a1d1782eecb05fde","tid":2094704,"uid":185652,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"rep